readable.content: A couple acting like they are swimming in front of a fish cutout door . A man and woman standing by a blue double door with fish and they are pretending to be swimming . A man dances as another holds her breath in front of a blue fish door . The two people in t-shirts pretend to swim in front of two blue doors . Two people pretending to be in the water next to a door with fish cutouts .
